     FABAWP2P IF  E           K        DISK
     F**ABBPL60 UF  E           K        DISK                      A
     FABAWP2U O   E           K        DISK
     E                    HYM         5  6 0
     E                    HIS        31  7 0
     E                    HWS        31  7 0
     E                    PP6        31  7 0
     I            DS
     I                                        1 2170HIS
